OL,5, A family has issued a plea for bone    
OL,6, marrow donors after their two-year-old 
OL,7, son was diagnosed with a rare cancer.  
OL,9,FDoctor's had described Elijah, from    
OL,10,FPontypridd, as a medical "mystery" and 
OL,11,Fwere unable to explain his constant    
OL,12,Fillness prior his diagnosis.           
OL,14,FChloe Jones, Elijah's mum and also a   
OL,15,Fnurse, said he has "never gone longer  
OL,16,Fthan two weeks" without becoming ill.  
OL,18,FElijah is now in need of a bone marrow 
OL,19,Ftransplant and his family are urging   
OL,20,Fpeople to help them find a match.      
